text: The Last House on the Left is a 1972 American horror movie. It was directed by Wes Craven and produced by Sean S. Cunningham. The movie stars Sandra Peabody, Lucy Grantham, David A. Hess, Fred Lincoln, Jeramie Rain, and Marc Sheffler. Category:1972 movies Category:English-language movies Category:American horror movies
title: The Last House on the Left
